{"tid":1438792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有網民疑開發起底警察程式涉教唆謀殺7月18被捕","createTime":"2019-08-10T01:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:30:17.000Z","uid":302888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa44f244628716c18fcbcba8cf3a81b04e2705eb","tid":1438792,"uid":302888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"據說他研發人工智能辨別警察程式，於7月18日被便衣沒出示委任證的&quot;警員&quot;所捕。在一輛沒有標記的車裏，被黑警嚴刑逼供，試圖強行臉部解鎖iphone，其後用軟件入侵他電腦錄下私隱...多次逼他解鎖iphone。被捕過程10小時多，后獲保釋。(但還是被便衣跟蹤)最近接受紐時跟蘋果訪問<br />\n<br />\n詳情請看紐時 and apple 為標準<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190729/hong-kong-protests-facial-recognition-surveillance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Ftechnology%2F20190729%2Fhong-kong-protests-facial-recognition-surveillance&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=43f97410\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190729/hong-kong-protests-facial-recognition-surveillance</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(寫得不好請見諒)</span>"}]}